对《德拉诺之王》的总体评价出现了一次波折。《德拉诺之王》在发售之初多获体验者和媒体的赞同评价，这在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]汇总的87分以及[[IGN|IGN]]给出的9.0分上有所体现<ref name="Metacritic Draenor">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/world-of-warcraft-warlords-of-draenor|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|title=World of Warcraft: Warlords of Draenor|accessdate=7 December 2014}}</ref>。IGN评价称“多元化的任务系统，自定义的要塞系统，美丽的新世界，强化的探索内容”是该资料片的优点，“单人内容过多”则是缺点。IGN还称，游戏每处细节都充满趣味，暴雪亦通过设计鼓励玩家们社交的策略有效避免了单人化的趋势，“《德拉诺之王》是一部足以令暴雪骄傲的资料片，他宣告着《魔兽世界》已凯旋归来”<ref name="12450a">{{Cite web|url = http://games.sina.com.cn/o/z/wow/2014-11-28/1135586322.shtml|title = 德拉诺之王资料片获IGN肯定 9.0高分评价送魔兽|accessdate = 2015-07-21|author = 佚名|date = 2014-11-28|publisher = 新浪魔兽世界专区}}</ref>；GamesRadar的Lucas Sullivan更将《德拉诺之王》称为“近年来最强的《魔兽世界》资料片”<ref name="G Radar" />。

在该资料片的中后期补丁发布后，游戏则遭到了部分尖锐的批评。在该资料片中，暴雪曾宣布永久禁止飞行，但立即遭到大量玩家反对<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.ithome.com/html/game/151333.htm|title = 《魔兽世界》全面禁飞，玩家怒喷500页帖|accessdate = 2015-07-21|author = 佚名|date = 2015-05-09|publisher = ITHOME|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150630173648/http://www.ithome.com/html/game/151333.htm|archivedate = 2015年6月30日|df = }}</ref>。暴雪迫于反对浪潮，在一个更新补丁中恢复了飞行内容<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.battlenet.com.cn/wow/zh/blog/17390517|title = 开发者和你聊：德拉诺飞行|accessdate = 2015-07-21|author = Ion Hazzikostas|date = 2015-06-11|publisher = 暴雪娱乐}}</ref>；亦有玩家将资料片中有争议的改动逐条列出<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://wow.tgbus.com/news/patch/201507/20150709093131.shtml|title = 花式打脸此文必火！史无前例的德拉诺之王|accessdate = 2015-07-21|author = 佚名|date = 2015-07-09|publisher = 电玩巴士}}</ref>。相比发售之初，资料片内容的缺失，苛刻的成就条件和不断推迟的重要补丁更新均招致恶评，暴雪则对此分别作出解释并着手改善<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url = http://wow.178.com/201508/233261246734.html|title = 魔兽蓝贴：玩家对现有飞行成就设定表示不满|accessdate = 2015-08-22|author = 暴雪娱乐|date = 2015-08-11|publisher = 178游戏网}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://w.163.com/15/0603/10/AR68QJBH00314C3U.html|title = 魔兽蓝推：本周设计师将解释WOD为何内容太少|accessdate = 2015-08-22|author = 暴雪娱乐|date = 2015-06-03|publisher = 网易|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304225739/http://w.163.com/15/0603/10/AR68QJBH00314C3U.html|archive-date = 2016-03-04|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://wow.178.com/201508/234123139813.html|title = 暴雪蓝贴：Lore对于为何这么迟才开飞行的回复|accessdate = 2015-08-22|author = tgr891002，暴雪娱乐|date = 2015-08-21|publisher = 178游戏网}}</ref>。在2015年8月21日的一次设计师访谈中，暴雪开发团队承认了《德拉诺之王》在上述设计上的“失败”<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://wow.duowan.com/1508/304084534261.html?_t=t|title = 21日设计师访谈 承认德拉诺之王的失败|accessdate = 2015-09-04|author = 壹米柒零，暴雪娱乐|date = 2015-08-21|publisher = 多玩}}</ref>。

=== 销量 ===

《德拉诺之王》在发售首天售出了超过330万份拷贝，活跃玩家数则从740万<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/10/15/world-of-warcraft-subscribers-hit-74-million-ahead-of-expansion|title=World of Warcraft subscribers hit 7.4 million ahead of expansion|last=Pitcher |first=Jenna|date=October 14, 2014|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=|accessdate=November 5, 2014}}</ref>突增至1050万<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2014/11/19/world-of-warcraft-tops-10-million-subscribers-following-warlords-of-draenor-expansion/|title='World Of Warcraft' Tops 10 Million Subscribers Following 'Warlords Of Draenor' Expansion|last=Kain|first=Erik|date=November 19, 2014|accessdate=November 20, 2014|archive-date=2016-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113190841/http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2014/11/19/world-of-warcraft-tops-10-million-subscribers-following-warlords-of-draenor-expansion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是暴雪财报显示在2015年第一季度末活跃玩家数已回落到710万，比该资料片发售前减少了30万<ref>[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]], ''[http://www.businessinsider.com/world-of-warcraft-lost-three-million-subscribers-in-three-months-2015-5|World World of Warcraft lost three million subscribers in three months]'', retrieved on May, 10th, 2015</ref>；6.2版本发布后的2015年第二季度末，活跃玩家数则回落到560万，此数值为《魔兽世界》上线运营后自2005年12月以来的新低<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://wow.tgbus.com/news/international/201508/20150805053200.shtml|title = 2015魔兽第二季度财报 付费用户减少150万降至560万|accessdate = 2015-08-05|author = MMO-Champion|date = 2015-08-05|publisher = 电玩巴士}}</ref>。之后的暴雪财报亦显示活跃玩家数量延续了自《大地的裂变》以来的下降趋势<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://wow.178.com/201511/240530279971.html|title = 暴雪公布2015年Q3财报 魔兽付费玩家现为550万|accessdate = 2015-11-06|author = tgr891002|date = 2015-11-03|publisher = 178游戏网}}</ref>。

